  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Myst is a graphic adventure puzzle game developed by Cyan and released in 1993.\nPlayers explore a mysterious island filled with interactive environments, books, and clues that reveal its story. The gameplay focuses on solving logic-based puzzles and uncovering the fate of two trapped brothers. It features pre-rendered visuals and a non-linear structure that encourages exploration and observation.\n\nMyst became one of the best-selling PC games of its era and influenced the adventure game genre.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Alone on a mysterious island, you set out to explore its grandeur and mystery. Hear how a chilling tale of intrigue and treachery, defying all boundaries of space and time, is being told.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
